<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Hours after revealing she's pregnant, Victoria's Secret Angel Elsa Hosk put her burgeoning baby bump on display at a coffee shop in Manhattan's SoHo neighborhood on Tuesday.</p>

<p>It will be the first child for the expecting 31-year-old and her long-haired blond boyfriend Tom Daly, who certainly stood out in a rainbow-striped shirt.</p>

<p>Elsa made sure to protect herself, her unborn child, and others from the coronavirus by wearing a mask - which New York Governor Andrew Cuomo made mandatory for all public outings way back on April 15.  </p>

